			"homepage-2":
				"Outside of programming, I enjoy sports like gravel cycling and volleyball, spending time with my",
			"homepage-3": "and friends, and playing video games",
			girlfriend: "girlfriend",
			"work-current-job": "Current job",
			"trelleborg-1":
				"In the company since 2021, I have had the opportunity to work in different organizations. Started as an Application Developer, mainly focused on building interfaces and extending our ERP functionalities.",
			"trelleborg-2":
